            <p>
                But we know that tutorials and articls are not enough to quickly grow your skillset as a developer.
                So, we created Mindsers Club to bring courses, community and personal coaching to accelerate your
                growth.
            </p>
            <p>
                Thank you for considering subscribing. Anyone is welcome in the Mindsers Club!
            </p>
        </header>
    </div>

    <section class='mds-plan-grid'>
